  m_Name: Lesson_PlayerInitiatedMovement_1
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  ClassroomTitle: Player Initiated Movement (Base)
  LessonSteps:
  - m_DialogueString: "Welcome to the Classroom. \r\nYou have just experienced the
      first variant of Player Initiated Movement. \r"
    m_ClearPreviousImage: 1
    m_MainImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: bfd070a869b6c3b4cbdd73c3d6de06ca, type: 3}
    m_VoiceoverClip: {fileID: 0}
  - m_DialogueString: Player Initiated Movement refers to the controls a user has
      to initiate movement in an application. This is highly important in Virtual
      Reality applications due to its immersive nature.
    m_ClearPreviousImage: 1
    m_MainImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 4bc0e11d3c7b93e419edc08f628c2a69, type: 3}
    m_VoiceoverClip: {fileID: 0}
  - m_DialogueString: "Hence, it is vital we understand the different variants of
      designing player initiated movement controls and their effects on users. \r"
    m_ClearPreviousImage: 1
    m_MainImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 4bc0e11d3c7b93e419edc08f628c2a69, type: 3}
    m_VoiceoverClip: {fileID: 0}
  - m_DialogueString: 'In VR, there are up to 6 degrees of freedom. '
    m_ClearPreviousImage: 1
    m_MainImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: f7ede7d64932faa4fa8688a47e3c2711, type: 3}
    m_VoiceoverClip: {fileID: 0}
  - m_DialogueString: "3 of these 6 degrees of freedom are rotational movement, as
      shown on the head. The remaining 3 are translational movement, as shown on
      the body\r."
    m_ClearPreviousImage: 1
    m_MainImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: f7ede7d64932faa4fa8688a47e3c2711, type: 3}
    m_VoiceoverClip: {fileID: 0}
  - m_DialogueString: "In this first level, you have navigated around using single
      axis movement controls with linear speed motion.\r"
    m_ClearPreviousImage: 1
    m_MainImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: b8faf5119957ef14ca6b5831f4fcec2d, type: 3}
    m_VoiceoverClip: {fileID: 0}
  - m_DialogueString: "By limiting the movements to a single axis of forward and
      back, it reduces one\u2019s sensitivity to motion and acceleration along axes.\r"
    m_ClearPreviousImage: 1
    m_MainImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: b8faf5119957ef14ca6b5831f4fcec2d, type: 3}
    m_VoiceoverClip: {fileID: 0}
  - m_DialogueString: "Next, you will be tasked to navigate through the same level,
      but with slightly different settings implemented.\r"
    m_ClearPreviousImage: 1
    m_MainImage: {fileID: 0}
    m_VoiceoverClip: {fileID: 0}
  - m_DialogueString: "Whenever you are ready, head to the door on your left. \r"
    m_ClearPreviousImage: 1
    m_MainImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 6f13ccda2f65ea04c9ea4559772ef214, type: 3}
    m_VoiceoverClip: {fileID: 0}
